data.description: Welcome to your inviting 3-bed, 2-bath Peoria home with an expansive nearly 1/4-acre backyard. This charming residence boasts a cozy living area, a well-appointed kitchen with gas appliances, and an extended patio overlooking the backyard, which is dirt-backed with potential to customize as you please. Nestled in a popular community, it's your ideal spot for comfortable living and outdoor creativity. Don't miss this chance to make it yours!
